         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. &amp; zool. Garden, ¶ 28. April ¶  ¶ 1861. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to sanction the sum of £700.- .- ¶  ¶ (seven hundred pounds Sterl.) to be expende...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.04.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Richard Heales</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">S61/3388, unit 749, VPRS 1189/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. &amp; zool. Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28. April<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1861.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to solicit, that you will be pleased to sanction the sum of £700.- .-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(seven hundred pounds Sterl.) to be expended, in addition to the £500.- .-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>already granted for the month of April, in wages for the current quarter of the year.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I further beg to solicit, that you will be pleased to place at my disposal the undermentioned sums for defraying the respective contingent expenses to be incurred during this quarter of the year and such as may remain unliquidated from last quarter vize:</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Purchase of plants and seeds</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£37.</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">10/</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Expense of publishing work on indigenous plants of Victoria</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£80.</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">- .</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Forage and food for animals</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£40.</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">- .</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Travelling and incidental expenses</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
                        xml:lang="en">£40.</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">- .</p>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.0555in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.0555in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: center; "
                        xml:lang="en">-</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obedient &amp; humble</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honor. the Chief Secretary.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's request was approved.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
